      { heading: "How Yurekh Solutions Can Help", content: "Yurekh Solutions specializes in website redesigns that preserve SEO while dramatically improving user experience and conversions. We start with a UX audit, then redesign with data-driven decisions, and migrate with zero downtime. Our redesigns typically improve conversion rates by 30–80%. Contact us for a free website audit." }
